# Network: Web App Chat

Network is a full-stack web chat application built using the MERN stack. Engage in real-time conversations, connect with peers, and be a part of the growing Network community.

## Features

- Real-time Chatting: Engage in real-time conversations with users.
- User Authentication: Secure signup and login functionality.
- Responsive Design: Optimized for both desktop and mobile devices.

## Technologies Used

- MongoDB: A NoSQL database.
- Express.js: Back-end web application framework running on top of Node.js.
- React: A JavaScript front-end library for building user interfaces.
- Node.js: JavaScript runtime built on Chrome's V8 JavaScript engine.
